<h3 id="Values" name="Values">Values</h3>
<dl><dt>
  &lt;br-style&gt;Â </dt>
 <dd>
  Is a keyword defined by <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-style" title=""><code>border-style</code></a> describing the style of the rule. The styling must be interpreted as in the collapsing border model.</dd>
